fortinet.name: fortinet

revisions.description: Added traps for RAID events and Power Supply Events.

Expanded traps to include sysName (hostname). Added new traps for other AV events, including oversize file blocking, file pattern matching, and fragmented file blocking. Renamed main AV trap to show actual usage.
Expanded vpn up/down traps and added OID's for local and remote gateway parameters. Updated Wifi platforms.
Added OID's for hdd usage and capacity. Added 5004 platform.
Added missing OID's for several traps used in communication between FortiGate and FortiManager. Also added some missing models. Moved fnIps group to correct OID.
Initial creation of unified MIB for products based on FortiOS >=3.00
